Capital Distribution Notice 
Commonfund Capital Partners V, L.P. 
 
 
 
 
March 26, 2024 
 
 
Dear Limited Partners, 
 
We are pleased to inform you of a $2.5 million cash distribution from Commonfund Capital 
Partners V, L.P., which will be sent on March 28, 2024. The attached schedule shows the 
amount each Partner has been allocated. This distribution brings total distributions to 
investors to $138.8 million on invested capital of $91.4 million, or a DPI of 1.52x. This 
distribution represents approximately 1% return of capital, 96% realized gains and 3% other 
income. The actual tax characterizations may vary from the distribution amount and will be 
reflected on your annual K-1 tax statement.  
 
The majority of the proceeds in this distribution are from: 
 
CFPE portfolio companies of Commonfund Capital Venture Partners X,L.P., 
Commonfund Capital Emerging Markets, 2013 L.P., Commonfund Capital Private Equity 
Partners VIII,L.P. 
 
Completed sale of RevSpring & the Sotera Health Company (NASDAQ:SHC) – GTCR 
Fund XI L.P. 
 
Please note that for certain limited partners, the distribution is being reduced for state 
taxes previously remitted by the fund. Those affected by this withholding should 
consult their tax advisor. 
 
Should you have any questions regarding this notice, please contact Kieran Duncan at (203) 
563-5065 
or 
via 
e-mail 
at 
kieran.duncan@cfprivateequity.com. 
Please 
contact 
notifications@cfprivateequity.com regarding access to the Client Reporting Portal. 
 
Sincerely, 
 
CF Private Equity
